                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2556-18420822 t18420822-2556-punishment-335"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder</hi>.</p>
